Australia dump 🇦🇺🦘
1. Jeevan ki pahli business class seat ( first of many ) 
2. Melbourne ki sadko pe paidal baazi 
3. Kangaroo namak jeev ko khana khilate hue 
4. Beer aur strawberry Philip island beach par 
5. Walking tour par Melbourne graffiti ke baare me samjhati hui Victoria mool ki mahila
6. Nakshebaazi 
7. Bradman-Tendulkar 🤝 
8. Hot pot namak restaurant se sakshatkar 
9. Sydney ke park me tanha fursat ke pal 
10. Coffee peene ki aadat lag gyi Aus jaake 
11. Sydney me Nepali khana ( Chowmein momos and my favourite sadeko ) 
12. Sydney ka sabse prachtit Ivy club me shukravaar ki shaam 
13. Party ke baad bhookhe Doston ko naye sheher me desi khana khilate hue . 
14. Over the wicket outswinger to left handed batsmen , danda bahar . 
15. Hukkah peene gye the Lekin bill padhke laga kuch galat jagah to nahi gye 
16. Melbourne ke uddhand pakshiyon ko uncle tetsu Japanese cake ke behtareen swaad aur fluffyness se avgat karwaya .

Iss video ke 1 lakh views ho gye , haalanki itna waqt internet pe guzarne ke baad mujhe ye to pata hai ki numbers se koi farak nahi padta aur koi bhi number bada nahi hota . 
Lekin iss video ka ek ek view ek ek comment mere liye uphaar Swaroop hai . 
8 saal se comedy aur internet pe content dalne ke baad Jis prakar ka prem aur atmiyta is video se mili hai wo atyant hi abhivoot karne wali hai. 
Kuch messages jo mujhe aaye wo main share kar rha hoon , kuch atyant personal the wo nahi kar paunga , Lekin sabhi log Jinko meri aur mummy ki baat cheet pasand aayi unke liye behad dhanyawaad . 
@tanejamainhoon bhai @weareyuvaa ki poori team ka bahut bahut shukriya mujhe ye mauka dene ke liye aur Itna sundar episode shoot aur edit karne ke liye

Jitne log abhi kisi bhi viprit paristithi se guzar rahe hain , haunsla rakhein , waqt badalta , humara Badla hai ♥️
